				\begin{document}$$S_{h}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M112"><mml:msub><mml:mi>S</mml:mi><mml:mi>h</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2020_3779_Article_IEq59.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>. The principle of generating <inline-formula id="IEq60"><alternatives><tex-math id="M113">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
