				\begin{document}$$s_{q}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M122"><mml:msub><mml:mi>s</mml:mi><mml:mi>q</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2020_3779_Article_IEq63.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>}, respectively. RepAHR checks how many <italic>k-mers</italic> in <italic>S</italic> appear in the high frequency <italic>k-mer</italic> set <inline-formula id="IEq64"><alternatives><tex-math id="M123">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
